{"tid":1018330,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美談判代表：3月1日貿易戰休兵期限不會延後","createTime":"2019-02-12T07:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T23:04:16.000Z","uid":81698,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ae4307c41979c99ad2fd57a5bd6dac162d14840e","tid":1018330,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T07:30:35.000Z","msg":"南華早報報導，在北京舉行的美中副部長級貿易協商12日進入第二天，美方談判代表、財政部主管國際事務的次長馬爾帕斯（David Malpass）表示，3月1日美中貿易戰休兵期限不會往後延。<br />\n<br />\n馬爾帕斯在走出下榻的飯店時被問到，休兵期限是否會延後，他簡單回答：「<span style=\"color: red;\">不會</span>。」馬爾帕斯已被川普總統提名為世界銀行總裁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/10511/3639552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F10511%2F3639552&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=0e30b580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/10511/3639552</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想快點3月1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69c4348935840be475255bc889f29a6e98c879a","tid":1018330,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T07:32:14.000Z","msg":"David Malpass, a member of the US trade delegation in Beijing, said on Tuesday that the looming March 1 deadline for China and the United States to reach a trade deal would not be extended.<br />\n<br />\nThe undersecretary for international affairs responded with a simple &ldquo;No&rdquo; to questions about whether the cut-off date would be pushed back, on his way out of his hotel in downtown Beijing for the second day of this week&rsquo;s talks."},{"pid":"5a2d9962a7f2f7ac44105b476861bb9732137489","tid":1018330,"uid":42190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198bc1a9ef39000891411d09cf129ebc3f8bd033","tid":1018330,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a2d9962a7f2f7ac